3. **Cancellation of the Policy**
   i. This Policy may be cancelled at any time by Us giving fourteen (14) days' notice by email or registered mail to Your last known address Such cancellation shall become effective from the first day of the month following the date of such notice issued and in such event, We will return a pro rata portion of the premium for the unexpired part of the Period of Insurance, provided no claim has been made under the Policy.
